                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.00/3763: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Third Secretary of Embassy in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wendelin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-11-14T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 14, 1936—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>191. Your X–311, November 13, 10 p.m. Please keep us informed as to action
                    British may take in order that we may be in a position to act promptly in the
                    event that similar action on our part seems advisable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
